===[[Pokémon Trading Card Game Pocket]]===
{{main|Koga (Genetic Apex 222)}}
Koga makes an appearance as a {{TCG|Supporter}} card in [[Pokémon Trading Card Game Pocket]]'s first expansion, {{TCGP|Genetic Apex}}. When the player plays this card, they may take a {{TCGP|Muk}} or {{TCGP|Weezing}} from the Active Spot and put it into their hand.

